snippet.title: Slumbering Feline - Step into the shoes of Momo - Available on Windows via Itch.io
snippet.description:
Slumbering Feline is a single-player, one-shot game featuring a feline-themed story. Step into the shoes of Momo, who finds herself lost in a strange dream and trying to escape from her slumber.

Waking up in an unfamiliar world, Momo is equipped with the mystical gear she’s always desired. Momo will explore, battle enemies, discover weak points, find the key, and make a daring escape. Can Momo find her way out of this dreamscape?

Slumbering Feline is currently available on Windows via Itch.io (coming soon to Steam)
In order to improve this game, any feedback is really appreciated.

Download via Itch.io: https://theflavare.itch.io/slumbering-feline

--
Development by The Flavare.
--
Music Nightmare by edamaaaaame88
